# Noetfield — SHIP CONTINUOUSLY (ASF)

**ASF:** Do not let anything block **progress** or **shipping**.  
**Do NOT:** stop working until the next user message or next Prompt OS task arrives.

## Ingest (clarified)

**Ingest** = sending your answers **into** Sina Prompt OS / execution-truth (ASF visibility).  
Ingest is **required hygiene**, not a blocker. A failed ingest on one repo ≠ stop the product sprint.

When possible, end IMPLEMENT replies with YAML per [docs/spec/EXECUTION_TRUTH_AGENT_REPLY_LOCKED.md](docs/spec/EXECUTION_TRUTH_AGENT_REPLY_LOCKED.md) including `reported_at`.

